/*
 * rkfb_hdmi_regs.h
 *
 * Neutral RK3399/RockPro64 HDMI register offsets for rkfb experiments.
 *
 * Scope:
 *   - Base address used on RockPro64 RK3399 experiments: 0xFF940000
 *   - Low offsets observed directly on the user's hardware
 *   - Additional offset groups that are publicly visible in Linux's
 *     generic Synopsys DesignWare HDMI driver/header, rewritten here with
 *     neutral offset-based names rather than Linux register names
 *
 * Intent:
 *   - Research / bring-up aid
 *   - Avoid Linux identifier reuse in FreeBSD-side experimental code
 *
 * Notes:
 *   - All offsets are byte offsets from the HDMI controller base.
 *   - "Observed" comments come from the user's live MMIO dumps.
 *   - Not all offsets below have been live-tested on this board yet.
 */

